DISTRIBUTING GAME BINARIES:

 - Linux, *BSD: ./configure --enable-all-static; make
 - BeOS: include SDL.so SDL_image.so SDL_ttf.so freetype2.so smpeg.so
 - MSVC: include SDL.dll SDL_image.dll jpeg.dll libpng1.dll zlib.dll
 - Cygwin: include 
     SDL.dll SDL_image.dll cygjpeg6b.dll cygpng12.dll cygwin1.dll cygz.dll

REMEMBER ABOUT THE LICENSE! (include README-SDL)